{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"5302","heading":"Purposes","label":"5302 Purposes","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/ch73","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5302","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments1998—Par. (3). added par. (3).Pub. L. 105–312"],"amendments":["Amendments1998—Par. (3). added par. (3).Pub. L. 105–312"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5302%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To assist in the conservation of rhinoceros and tigers by supporting the conservation programs of nations whose activities directly or indirectly affect rhinoceros and tiger populations, and the CITES Secretariat.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5302%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To provide financial resources for those programs.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t16/s5302","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft16%2Fs5302%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To prohibit the sale, importation, and exportation of products intended for human consumption or application containing, or labeled or advertised as containing, any substance derived from any species of rhinoceros or tiger.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
